who_is_responsible: Model developed by Nicholas Kluge ([nicholas@airespucrs.org](mailto:nicholas@airespucrs.org)), researcher at the Pontifical Catholic University of Rio Grande do Sul (PUCRS), in October 2022;
model_specification: This model is a Convolutional Neural Network trained in multi-label classification;
intended_use: This model was trained solely for academic motivations, in order to explore interpretability techniques and adversarial example generation in ML;
dataset: The dataset used to train this model was the CIFAR-10 dataset (Canadian Institute For Advanced Research);
